M|marketing-ideas|When recommending ideas, provide for each:
M|marketing-ideas|- **Idea name**: One-line description
M|marketing-ideas|- **Why it fits**: Connection to their situation
M|marketing-ideas|- **How to start**: First 2-3 implementation steps
M|marketing-ideas|- **Expected outcome**: What success looks like
M|marketing-ideas|- **Resources needed**: Time, budget, skills required
M|marketing-ideas|1. What's your current stage and main growth goal?
